        <unitName xml:lang="en">m3/kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Measured value. Amount of volcanic ash, accounted for together with sand, used to produce 1kg of concrete block, according to the information provided by the owner of the factory. No losses considered.</comment>
